Reasoning: The paper discusses the growing role of intellectual capital within organizations and its impact on knowledge management and competence development. It proposes a multilayer diffusion model for competence development through horizontal and vertical knowledge diffusion in a network of agents. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for modeling cognitive abilities, social intelligence (cs.SI) for modeling social interactions, machine learning (cs.LG) for analyzing competence development, cybersecurity (cs.CY) for managing knowledge security, and systems and control (cs.SY) for modeling complex systems.
